# Project Checklist

## 1. Project Setup & Dependencies
-------------------------------------------------
### 1. Initial Setup
- [ ] Create new Next.js project with TypeScript
- [ ] Configure project structure (/app, /components, /lib, etc.)
- [ ] Initialize Git repository
- [ ] Create .gitignore file

### 2. UI Development - Core Dependencies
- [ ] Install and configure Tailwind CSS
- [ ] Set up shadcn/ui components
- [ ] Install Lucide icons
- [ ] Configure ESLint and Prettier
- [ ] Set up TypeScript configuration
- [ ] Install development dependencies (testing libraries, etc.)

### 3. Environment Configuration
- [ ] Create development environment (.env.development)
- [ ] Create production environment (.env.production)
- [ ] Set up environment variable validation
- [ ] Document all environment variables

### 4. Design System
- [ ] Set up color palette in Tailwind config
- [ ] Create typography system
- [ ] Define spacing/sizing scales
- [ ] Create reusable button styles
- [ ] Define form component styles
- [ ] Create animation utilities

## 2. Accessibility
-------------------------------------------------
- [ ] Implement keyboard navigation
- [ ] Add ARIA labels and roles
- [ ] Ensure proper heading hierarchy
- [ ] Test with screen readers
- [ ] Add skip-to-main content link
- [ ] Implement focus management

## 3. Page Development
-------------------------------------------------
### * Core Pages
- [ ] Create homepage layout
- [ ] Build about page
- [ ] Implement contact page
- [ ] Create privacy policy page
- [ ] Build terms of service page
- [ ] Design 404 error page

### * Dynamic Pages
- [ ] Set up dynamic routing
- [ ] Implement loading states
- [ ] Create error handling
- [ ] Add pagination (if needed)
- [ ] Configure data fetching
- [ ] Implement caching strategy

## 4. Deployment & Infrastructure
-------------------------------------------------
### * Development Environment
- [ ] Set up local development workflow
- [ ] Configure hot reloading
- [ ] Set up development database
- [ ] Create development API endpoints

### * Production Deployment
- [ ] Configure Cloudflare Pages
- [ ] Set up custom domain
- [ ] Configure SSL certificates
- [ ] Set up CDN caching
